text: Field Marshal Sarit Thanarat (Thai: สฤษดิ์ ธนะรัชต์, 16 June 1908 – 8 December 1963) was a Thai general. He staged a coup in 1957 and then became prime minister until he died in 1963. == References == Category:1908 births Category:1963 deaths Category:Prime ministers of Thailand
title: Sarit Thanarat
